Tara McIntyre was left virtually wheelchair-bound after Ben Hagon's Mercedes sports car crashed into her . 
  She suffered a fractured spine and pelvis and was left with life-changing injuries at Chelmsford Crown Court . 
  Hagon was more than twice the legal alcohol limit and was jailed for two years eight months . 
  He had taken prescription tranquilisers and was drinking at the time of the crash . 
  He was driving at up to 75mph when he hit Miss McIntyre in Essex . 
  Judge branded his driving 'madness' and sentenced him to two years and eight months in prison . 
 